{"id":"aeeda5ac-5272-45a7-be99-220c2e256908","name":"Aelor | Mermaid","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">You don’t remember much after falling off your ship, but the mermaid you woke beside claims he pulled you ashore. Unfortunately, in his eyes, that means you're his to keep.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/w6GashYpdydhcbcLl8MLX.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/JEb0_cXKM01Nk_-K_g0Bd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5K360mMepWScYDzuwp9j0.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HeZwULWGZKPS9Kk7yGEVq.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 628px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 241);\">During a storm, you fell off your ship into the lurching sea, left to meet your doom. Water filled your lungs and the currents dragged you under, you don't remember much after that. When you wake, you're on the beach of a deserted island, somewhere in French Polynesia. What surprises you isn't the fact that you're alive, but rather who saved you.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 241);\">Aelor, your new fishy friend, explains to you that he pulled you out of the water. Unfortunately for you, he's never been this close to a human before, and he's <em>awfully</em> curious about the differences between your bodies. Finders keepers, and he'll do anything to keep his new pet satisfied. He'll go on land to pick fruit for you, hunt fish for you in the water, and bring you the prettiest seashells he can find.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FBmThZFAE28HYySQQeNcl.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 628px;\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(229, 169, 191);\">˗</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(233, 177, 196);\">ˏ</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(237, 184, 201);\">ˋ</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(241, 192, 206);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 199, 211);\">꒰</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(249, 207, 216);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(253, 214, 221);\">y</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(251, 214, 220);\">e</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(248, 215, 219);\">l</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(246, 215, 219);\">l</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(243, 216, 218);\">o</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(241, 216, 217);\">w</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(243, 216, 218);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 215, 218);\">f</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(247, 215, 219);\">l</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(249, 215, 220);\">a</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(251, 214, 220);\">g</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(253, 214, 221);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(248, 205, 215);\">꒱</span><span style=\"font-s